title: Chinese Diplomat Meets Trump, Holds White House Talks - WSJ
text:
Chinese Diplomat Meets Trump, Holds White House Talks State Councilor Yang Jiechi is highest-ranking Chinese official to meet with members of administration By @felschwartz Feb. 27, 2017 5:15 p.m. ET 
WASHINGTON—China’s top diplomat briefly met President Donald Trump on Monday during a visit to Washington that comes as the two countries move to improve relations roiled by Mr. Trump’s harsh campaign stances toward Beijing. 
State Councilor Yang Jiechi became the highest-ranking Chinese official to meet with administration officials since Mr. Trump took office. His visit also comes as Mr. Trump charts a course on North Korea policy... To Read the Full Story, Subscribe or Sign In Most Popular Videos
